sentences.english: Avoid hard-coding blank spaces or tabs at the end of a line of sample code.
sentences.chinese: 要避免在示例代碼行的結尾用硬編碼空格或製表符。

sentences.english: This field is blank padded and is not null terminated.
sentences.chinese: 該字段用空格填充，且不以空字符結尾。

sentences.english: Thetwist at the end is especially noteworthy.
sentences.chinese: 結尾筆鋒一轉尤爲引人注目。

sentences.english: Only the initial letter in the first word of any complimentary close is capitalized.
sentences.chinese: 任何結尾謙稱用語都只大寫第一個字的第一個字母。

sentences.english: A burst of hand-clapping followed the ending of the story.
sentences.chinese: 在故事的結尾爆發了一陣陣掌聲。

sentences.english: Let me end with a couple of other quick remarks.
sentences.chinese: 讓我用一些其它的短評論來做結尾。

sentences.english: The Coda features the tune combined with an evocative countermelody in the piano.
sentences.chinese: 結尾部分的特徵在於結合了鋼琴的對位旋律。

sentences.english: There are 4 carbons in the longest chain ( but ) with no carbon-carbon double bonds ( ane ).
sentences.chinese: 首先沒有雙鍵，是烷烴，所以結尾應是。

sentences.english: No special handing for a missing end of line marker at the end of the file is provided.
sentences.chinese: 對於檔結尾缺少的行尾標記，不提供特殊的處理。

sentences.english: Kira: Don't tell me anything about it, especially spoilers .
sentences.chinese: 什麼也不要告訴我，尤其是有關電視劇結尾的信息。

sentences.english: At the end of the story, Seigo and Asako were attending the funeral of a friend.
sentences.chinese: 故事的結尾是省吾和志麻子一起去參加一個朋友葬禮。

sentences.english: At the conclusion of the program, the enterprise is in the to-be state defined by the program.
sentences.chinese: 在程序的結尾，企業就處在程序定義的完成狀態中。

sentences.english: Put the hyphen character at the start or the end of the bracketed list.
sentences.chinese: 將連字符放在中括號列表的開始或結尾。

sentences.english: By the end of the story, the Grinch becomes a kind person.
sentences.chinese: 到了故事的結尾，聖誕怪傑變成一個善良的人。

sentences.english: At the end of the story, the protagonist emerges as a powerful pugilist.
sentences.chinese: 在故事的結尾，主角變成了一個強有力的拳擊家。

sentences.english: In the conclusion part, some improvable aspects were pointed out.
sentences.chinese: 在文章的結尾，結合本次研究提出了幾點改進意見。
